high_descs: Move to the counter in between the two sinks
Pick up the soap from the counter
Move to the sink on the right from you
Clean the soap in the sink
Move to the counter in between the two sinks
Put the soap on the counter
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned bar of soap on a counter.

high_descs: Turn around and turn right to go to the sinks.
Pick up the bar of soap from in between the sinks.
Take a step to the right to face the sink.
Place the soap in the sink, turn the water on and then off. Pick up the soap.
Carry the soap and take a step to the left.
Place the soap on the counter in between the sinks.
anns.task_desc: Rinse off a bar of soap and place it on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around and begin walking across the room, then turn right and walk up to the sink counter.
Pick up the bar of soap that is on the counter in between the two sinks.
Turn around and take a step forward, then turn left and take another step, turn left again to face the sink.
Put the bar of soap into the rightmost sink basin and turn on the water, after a couple seconds turn the water off and remove the now clean bar of soap.
Turn left and take a step forward, then turn right to face the counter.
Place the clean bar of soap on front of the counter in between the two sinks.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean bar of soap on the bathroom counter.

high_descs: Turn around and go right towards the double sings.
Pick up the bar of soap.
Go to the right and face the sink.
Put the bar of soap in the sink, turn the water on and then off and then pick up the bar of soap.
Move to the left.
Put the soap down in between the two sinks.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean bar of soap on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the sinks.
Pick up the soap from in between the sinks.
Move to the right to face the rightmost sink.
Get the soap wet in the sink.
Move back to the left.
Put the soap in between the two sinks.
anns.task_desc: Put wet soap in between the sinks.
